headline: Cold Weather Causes These Stocks To Rally. Reported Merger Talks Add To Gains.
summary: The price of natural gas rebounded sharply Tuesday, causing several natgas stocks to rally.  If you're stuck at home because of bitterly cold weather, you already understand why.  Front-month natural gas prices jumped nearly 24%, or 74 cents, to $3.843 per million British thermal units.
